casebody.data:
Monday, July 11, 1994

MOTION DOCKET

94-642, 94-643 and 94-644. Gen. Motors Corp. v. Tracy.

Board of Tax Appeals, Nos. 92-K-146, 92-K-510 and 91-K-1558. This cause is pending before the court on an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals.

Upon consideration of appellant’s motion to allow access to sealed record,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion be, and hereby is, granted, effective July 8, 1994.
